100
00:06:34,900 --> 00:06:37,100
Awak sengaja bawa dia lari daripada saya ke?

101
00:06:37,100 --> 00:06:38,960
Awak dah minum beberapa gelas ke?

102
00:06:39,220 --> 00:06:40,940
Baliklah ke bilik dan berehat.

103
00:06:40,940 --> 00:06:42,500
Satu lagi saya nak beritahu awak.

104
00:06:42,500 --> 00:06:44,380
Kalau tak nak hidup awak jadi kucar-kacir,

105
00:06:44,380 --> 00:06:45,380
