106
00:06:45,740 --> 00:06:46,780
Bos kecil.

107
00:06:48,659 --> 00:06:49,820
Itu suara Chonlada.

108
00:06:49,820 --> 00:06:51,020
Kak Nam, awak di mana?

109
00:06:54,860 --> 00:06:57,460
Err, saya ada kerja. Nanti kita sambung lagi.

110
00:07:00,420 --> 00:07:01,340
Hei, awak.

111
00:07:01,580 --> 00:07:04,180
Tak nampak ke saya tengah bercakap di telefon?

112
00:07:05,060 --> 00:07:06,220
Nampak.

113
00:07:06,220 --> 00:07:07,740
Sebab awak tak nampak kewujudan saya,

114
00:07:07,740 --> 00:07:10,070
sebab itulah saya kena muncul depan awak.

115
00:07:10,260 --> 00:07:11,220
Saya tak faham.

116
00:07:11,220 --> 00:07:14,220
Kenapa awak suruh saya tunggu dalam bilik mesyuarat?

117
00:07:18,100 --> 00:07:19,260
Kalau tak ada apa-apa lagi,

118
00:07:19,260 --> 00:07:20,860
