119
00:07:20,860 --> 00:07:22,500
Sebab Kak Nuch kata

120
00:07:22,500 --> 00:07:23,960
Cik Wayo datang cari saya.

121
00:07:25,980 --> 00:07:26,820
Nak buat apa?

122
00:07:27,460 --> 00:07:28,820
Kak Nuch kata

123
00:07:28,820 --> 00:07:30,620
Cik Wayo datang cari saya.

124
00:07:31,140 --> 00:07:31,820
Hmm.

125
00:07:33,900 --> 00:07:35,760
Habis tu, awak nak turun buat apa?

126
00:07:36,420 --> 00:07:38,220
Nak uruskan hal penginapanlah.

127
00:07:39,980 --> 00:07:42,300
Saya dah beritahu Wadee untuk uruskan hal penginapan itu.

128
00:07:42,300 --> 00:07:43,420
Tak payah pergi.

129
00:07:43,980 --> 00:07:45,540
Saya dah cakap.

130
00:07:45,540 --> 00:07:48,659
Tapi Kak Nuch tetap kata Cik Wayo nak jumpa saya.

131
00:07:49,340 --> 00:07:51,740
Cik Wayo ialah tetamu hotel ini.

132
00:07:51,740 --> 00:07:53,620
Lagipun, dia adik perempuan bos.

133
00:07:54,100 --> 00:07:56,560
Saya tak nak didenda sebab cuai dalam tugas.

134
00:07:57,180 --> 00:07:58,540
Saya pergi dulu, bos.

135
00:08:02,060 --> 00:08:03,020
Duduk sini.

136
00:08:03,380 --> 00:08:04,460
Aduh.

137
00:08:05,420 --> 00:08:07,580
Duduk sini dan senyap.

138
00:08:07,580 --> 00:08:09,860
Nanti saya balik, saya ada kerja untuk awak.

139
00:08:09,860 --> 00:08:11,540
-Tapi, bos kecil... -Hei!

140
00:08:14,780 --> 00:08:17,420
Kalau awak ingkar arahan saya sekali lagi,

141
00:08:17,820 --> 00:08:19,350
saya pasti akan pecat awak.

142
00:08:19,620 --> 00:08:21,220
Tak kira awak nak ugut atau saman saya,

143
00:08:21,220 --> 00:08:22,900
