144
00:08:22,900 --> 00:08:24,060
saya tak takut pun.

145
00:08:34,140 --> 00:08:35,299
Kejamnya.

146
00:08:38,179 --> 00:08:38,980
Hmph.

147
00:08:40,260 --> 00:08:41,919
Awak risaukan adik awak, kan?

148
00:08:42,419 --> 00:08:43,340
Baguslah.

149
00:08:44,179 --> 00:08:47,900
Bawa sajalah saya ke mana-mana, bos kecil.

150
00:09:28,940 --> 00:09:29,780
Helo.

151
00:10:01,140 --> 00:10:02,460
Siapalah agaknya orang ni?

152
00:10:02,460 --> 00:10:05,190
Boleh pula dia tidur di tempat yang tak dikenali.

153
00:11:46,340 --> 00:11:47,580
Pukul tiga pagi.

154
00:11:53,900 --> 00:11:57,340
Kalau awak dah bangun, awak boleh balik. Tak perlu kejutkan saya.

155
00:11:57,340 --> 00:12:00,380
Lagi satu, panggil mak cik pembersih untuk bersihkan tempat ni.

156
00:12:00,380 --> 00:12:03,340
Lakukan rawatan ozon untuk elakkan sofa berkulat.

157
00:12:03,340 --> 00:12:04,900
Awak tidur sampai terliur.

158
00:12:08,540 --> 00:12:10,420
Saya taklah selekeh macam tu.

159
00:12:49,020 --> 00:12:50,660
Awak kata saya selekeh?

160
00:12:51,620 --> 00:12:52,540
Baiklah.

161
00:13:11,180 --> 00:13:13,100
Blehh.

162
00:13:30,580 --> 00:13:32,060
Masih ada orang di dalam.

163
00:13:45,060 --> 00:13:46,820
Ini pasti berita besar.

164
00:13:48,660 --> 00:13:51,940
[Wanna: Bos kecil dan pekerja baharu berada di bilik mesyuarat sehingga hampir pagi.]

165
00:13:51,940 --> 00:13:55,780
[Hotel Monarch]

166
00:14:18,660 --> 00:14:19,820
Lada.

167
00:14:19,980 --> 00:14:20,820
Kak Nuch.

168
00:14:21,100 --> 00:14:22,820
Awalnya awak sampai.

169
00:14:22,980 --> 00:14:24,820
Saya dah tunggu awak sekejap.

170
00:14:25,020 --> 00:14:26,140
Tunggu saya?

171
00:14:26,780 --> 00:14:28,300
Kenapa tunggu saya?

172
00:14:28,740 --> 00:14:29,900
Jangan-jangan...

173
00:14:30,860 --> 00:14:32,900
Bos kecil ada suruh saya buat apa-apa lagi ke?

174
00:14:32,900 --> 00:14:33,860
Ya.

175
00:14:33,860 --> 00:14:34,900
Ada kaitan dengan bos kecil,

176
00:14:34,900 --> 00:14:36,540
tapi bukan hal kerja.

177
00:14:39,140 --> 00:14:40,780
Kalau bukan hal kerja,

178
00:14:42,140 --> 00:14:43,700
