179
00:14:44,300 --> 00:14:46,760
Jadi, kamu berdua tidur bersama atau tidak?

180
00:14:50,700 --> 00:14:52,340
Maaf, cuma...

181
00:14:52,340 --> 00:14:53,060
Ini...

182
00:14:53,260 --> 00:14:55,460
Semua orang dah sebarkan gosip sampai macam ni ke?

183
00:14:55,460 --> 00:14:58,540
Tak ada sesiapa ke yang fikir saya dan bos kecil dalam pejabat

184
00:14:58,540 --> 00:15:00,200
sedang bincangkan hal kerja?

185
00:15:01,420 --> 00:15:05,580
Awak dan bos kecil keluar dari pejabat selepas pukul 3:00 pagi.

186
00:15:05,740 --> 00:15:08,000
Saya pun susah nak percaya itu hal kerja.

187
00:15:08,260 --> 00:15:11,700
Tapi saya dah kerja di Kumpulan Watin selama beberapa tahun.

188
00:15:11,700 --> 00:15:13,500
Selain Cik Preem,

189
00:15:13,780 --> 00:15:18,510
saya tak pernah nampak sesiapa yang dipanggil bincang kerja lewat malam macam awak.

190
00:15:20,780 --> 00:15:22,100
Tak pernah?

191
00:15:23,100 --> 00:15:24,260
Tak ada.

192
00:15:24,460 --> 00:15:26,420
Lagipun, tak ada seorang pun pekerja

193
00:15:26,420 --> 00:15:30,180
yang berani lawan cakap bos kecil macam awak tapi tak dipecat.

194
00:15:30,940 --> 00:15:32,380
Tambahan pula, bos kecil

195
00:15:32,660 --> 00:15:35,790
lebih rela bercakap dengan awak berbanding orang lain.

196
00:15:36,900 --> 00:15:38,580
Err, cuma...

197
00:15:39,100 --> 00:15:39,820
Cuma...

198
00:15:40,220 --> 00:15:41,260
Kak Nuch.

199
00:15:41,460 --> 00:15:42,860
Kak Nuch, dengar cakap saya.

200
00:15:42,860 --> 00:15:45,260
-Sebenarnya... -Sekarang hampir semua pekerja

201
00:15:45,260 --> 00:15:49,020
percaya yang awak dan bos kecil dah ada apa-apa.

202
00:15:52,140 --> 00:15:54,780
Walaupun awak nak jelaskan apa-apa sekarang, saya rasa

203
00:15:54,780 --> 00:15:56,460
mungkin tak ada orang akan dengar.

204
00:15:56,460 --> 00:15:57,820
Tengok mulut saya ya.

205
00:15:58,300 --> 00:15:59,580
Mustahil.

206
00:16:09,300 --> 00:16:11,940
Tapi saya tak nak nafikan apa-apa pun.

207
00:16:15,980 --> 00:16:17,900
Apa maksud awak, Lada?

208
00:16:18,740 --> 00:16:19,740
Jadi...

209
00:16:20,620 --> 00:16:22,380
hal awak dengan bos kecil tu,

210
00:16:23,300 --> 00:16:24,500
betul ke?

211
00:16:26,660 --> 00:16:28,580
Alahai, Kak Nuch.

212
00:16:28,580 --> 00:16:31,580
Saya kan perempuan, kalau cakap pun saya akan

213
00:16:32,060 --> 00:16:33,740
rasa malulah.

214
00:16:34,100 --> 00:16:35,260
Pendek kata,

215
00:16:35,660 --> 00:16:39,380
hal macam ni, biarlah bos kecil yang jawab sendiri.

216
00:16:55,420 --> 00:16:56,500
Jadi...

217
00:16:58,140 --> 00:16:59,420
Dah berapa kali buat?

218
00:17:03,980 --> 00:17:06,460
Saya tak nak makanlah.

219
00:17:06,460 --> 00:17:08,060
Pergi kerja.

220
00:17:08,060 --> 00:17:09,060
Baik.

221
00:17:09,060 --> 00:17:10,500
-Pergi kerja. -Baik.

222
00:17:18,660 --> 00:17:22,060
Preem, kebelakangan ini, ada apa-apa masalah dengan pekerja ke?

223
00:17:22,060 --> 00:17:23,780
Sejak saya masuk ke hotel,

224
00:17:23,780 --> 00:17:26,380
saya rasa macam semua pekerja pandang saya, kemudian berpaling dan bercakap sesuatu.

225
00:17:26,380 --> 00:17:28,580
Seperti berbisik-bisik tentang saya.

226
00:17:28,900 --> 00:17:31,340
Mungkin sebab khabar angin dalam hotel ini.

227
00:17:31,340 --> 00:17:33,980
Tapi saya betul-betul tak tahu siapa yang mulakannya.

228
00:17:33,980 --> 00:17:36,180
Khabar angin tentang apa?

229
00:17:38,940 --> 00:17:40,620
Ah, bos.

230
00:17:41,260 --> 00:17:42,180
Bos kecil.

231
00:17:47,260 --> 00:17:48,860
Bos kecil, awak tak apa-apa?

232
00:17:51,660 --> 00:17:52,700
Saya tak apa-apa.

233
00:18:01,660 --> 00:18:03,100
[Lom]

234
00:18:04,900 --> 00:18:05,940
[Lom]

235
00:18:09,700 --> 00:18:12,960
Cik Lom telefon untuk tanya tentang khabar angin itu, kan?

